---
---
<section class="section bg-dark">
    <div class="container testimonials-wrapper fade-up">
        <div class="quote-mark serif">"</div>
        <div id="test-slider">
            <div class="test-item active">
                <h3 class="serif">El lugar es muy lindo, elegante y te atienden literalmente como una reina. Excelente servicio.</h3>
                <p>— María G.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="test-item">
                <h3 class="serif">El mejor balayage de Guadalajara. Entendieron perfecto lo que quería y cuidaron mi cabello.</h3>
                <p>— Ana Sofía L.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="test-item">
                <h3 class="serif">Profesionalismo total. Salgo feliz con mi color y el trato te invita a regresar siempre.</h3>
                <p>— Carmen R.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="test-controls">
            <button id="t-prev">Ant</button> / <button id="t-next">Sig</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<style>
.bg-dark {
    background-color: var(--text-dark);
    color: var(--bg-color);
    padding: 10rem 0;
}
.testimonials-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}
.quote-mark {
    font-size: 8rem;
    line-height: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    opacity: 0.5;
}
.test-item {
    display: none;
    animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease;
}
.test-item.active {
    display: block;
}
.test-item h3 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
}
.test-item p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--accent-light);
}
.test-controls {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
}
.test-controls button {
    background: none; border: none; color: inherit; font: inherit; cursor: pointer; padding: 0.5rem; transition: color 0.3s;
}
.test-controls button:hover { color: var(--accent); }

@keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
</style>
<script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
        const items = document.querySelectorAll('.test-item');
        let current = 0;
        const next = document.getElementById('t-next');
        const prev = document.getElementById('t-prev');
        if(!next || items.length === 0) return;
        
        function show(i) {
            items.forEach(el => el.classList.remove('active'));
            items[i].classList.add('active');
        }
        
        next.addEventListener('click', () => {
            current = (current + 1) % items.length;
            show(current);
        });
        prev.addEventListener('click', () => {
            current = (current - 1 + items.length) % items.length;
            show(current);
        });
    });
</script>
